{"tid":1047563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳詠謙（毒瘤）最新作品《聲音導航》 受害者：馮允謙","createTime":"2019-03-05T04:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T04:57:17.000Z","uid":104218,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61efda00f6c0058821fbc293e41eaba6ecf17095","tid":1047563,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">詞：陳詠謙</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n編：周錫漢 / 黃兆銘<br />\n監：周錫漢<br />\n <br />\n是否太多想法未確定<br />\n或者擔子很重未適應<br />\n要在明日置身甚麼天地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不知究竟</span></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">（究竟可以咁用㗎咩）</span><br />\n <br />\n有把熟悉聲線在帶路<br />\n讓我在你心裡作嚮導<br />\n我願陪著你找幸福影像<br />\n騰雲駕霧<br />\n浮華亂世尋樂土<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">何地何方</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">（地方就地方啦向到&lsquo;啞&rsquo;字數</span> 釋放你的光芒<br />\n隨遇而安 不作定案<br />\n無定向 告別昨天 坐青春的客艙<br />\n何地何方 搜索你的天堂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">虛構著</span>眼前盛況<span style=\"color: blue;\">（虛構名詞黎呀點虛構著）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">環遊大腦</span> 鬆開眉頭 傳來暖光<span style=\"color: blue;\">（環遊世界我就聽過 環你老母大腦咩</span><br />\n有你專心聽我講<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">未算伴侶先變做伴旅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就趁白晝fly you to the moon</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">（填唔到中文直頭寫英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n閉目橫越太空跟你排憂解悶<br />\n何其壯觀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有苦有難</span>都不管<span style=\"color: blue;\">（苦難就苦難啦屌）</span><br />\n <br />\n何地何方 釋放你的光芒<br />\n隨遇而安 不作定案<br />\n無定向 告別昨天 坐青春的客艙<br />\n何地何方 搜索你的天堂<br />\n虛構著眼前盛況<br />\n環遊大腦 鬆開眉頭 傳來暖光<br />\n情迷意亂望前方<br />\n <br />\n何地何方 總要帶點瘋狂<br />\n隨遇而安 即興近況<br />\n離地了 再沒掣肘 去不知的<span style=\"color: red;\">國邦</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">（國邦姓咩呀）</span><br />\n何地何方 總有你的天堂<br />\n心繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">好奇熱燙</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯求讓我 聲音陪同 雲層透光<br />\n沿路照耀著前方"},{"pid":"292a78b7916fbd762f5c9035ba955d0fddd4f1c1","tid":1047563,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a052cc98909fea206d515a6da2e1739e5a9b7cb9","tid":1047563,"uid":104218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一日毒瘤終身毒瘤<br />\n你現時自己肯收皮未<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"67a8e24b4c6cb2b74d36a74a5e6b439d778d9dbc","tid":1047563,"uid":62822,"